   <S PAR='84' RSNT='1' SNO='84'>Prophesying in 1 Corinthians 14 is not in the sense of predicting.</S>
   <S PAR='85' RSNT='1' SNO='85'>Someone who prophesies might speak something like this: Brothers, 1 Corinthians 15:45b says, The last Adam became a life-giving Spirit.</S>
