   <S PAR='113' RSNT='1' SNO='113'>If we do not have a change, we are behind the times.</S>
   <S PAR='114' RSNT='1' SNO='114'>We cannot change the truth of the Scriptures, the Lord Jesus, and God s salvation, but we must change the way we minister the word of truth and practice the church life to the scriptural way, the God-ordained way, which is the best way.</S>
