   <S PAR='206' RSNT='1' SNO='206'>The saints will have an organic feeling to go out to reach people and get them baptized.</S>
   <S PAR='207' RSNT='1' SNO='207'>Without any need of organization or arrangement, the saints will have the burden to go to the homes of the new believers to take care of them.</S>
   <S PAR='208' RSNT='1' SNO='208'>Furthermore, they will have the burden to take care of the small group meetings organically, and they will have the organic motive to function, to prophesy, to speak for the Lord, in the church meetings.</S>
   <S PAR='209' RSNT='1' SNO='209'>We have to realize that we are far behind the biblical revelation in our practice of the church life.</S>
   <S PAR='210' RSNT='1' SNO='210'>Twenty-six years ago, I came to the United States with a burden to bring the Lord s recovery here, but the saints came into a recovery that was still, to a certain extent, remaining in tradition.</S>
